          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Client Renewals</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">Engagements end and clients don't always renew or continue.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Solution Section -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">
          How We Help Executive Coaches
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600">
          Nurture prospects, streamline discovery, and generate referrals while maintaining authentic connection.
