          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Discovery Automation</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">Streamlined scheduling and pre-call preparation maximize every conversation.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-700">
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Self-scheduling</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Pre-call prep</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Follow-up sequences</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-fuchsia-50 to-purple-50 p-8 rounded-2xl">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-fuchsia-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
